0Siddaramaiah%20on%20Saturday%2C%20February%2024%2C%20urged%20people%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20to%20tolerate%20defamation%20against%20the%20Constitution%E2%80%9D%20and%20instead%20bring%20to%20power%20%E2%80%9Cthose%20who%20respect%20the%20Constitution.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20the%20responsibility%20of%20every%20government%20to%20eradicate%20inequality%20in%20the%20country.%20Dr%20Ambedkar%2C%20the%20chief%20architect%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20understood%20what%20was%20needed%20for%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20Siddaramaiah%20said%2C%20while%20speaking%20at%20a%20two-day%20convention%20organised%20by%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20in%20Bengaluru%20to%20commemorate%20the%2075th%20year%20of%20the%20adoption%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20minister%20underlined%20that%20a%20society%20with%20social%20and%20economic%20inequality%20and%20political%20democracy%20can%20succeed%20only%20when%20it%20rests%20on%20the%20foundations%20of%20social%20democracy.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20the%20duty%20of%20every%20government%20to%20successfully%20and%20respectfully%20follow%20the%20articles%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%2C%20instead%20of%20changing%20or%20altering%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddaramaiah%20also%20released%20a%20special%20cover%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20Chief%20Post%20Master%20General%2C%20commemorating%2075%20years%20of%20the%20constitution%20while%20Basavaraj%20Horatti%2C%20chairman%20of%20the%20Karnataka%20Legislative%20Assembly%2C%20lead%20the%20audience%20in%20the%20reading%20of%20the%20Preamble%20at%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftake-nothing-for-granted-not-even-the-constitution%5C%22%3ETake%20Nothing%20for%20Granted%2C%20Not%20Even%20the%20Constitution%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20last%20one%20month%2C%20the%20state%20government%20has%20organised%20several%20initiatives%20that%20increased%20citizen%20awareness%20of%20the%20constitution%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20H.C.%20Mahadevappa%2C%20Karnataka%20minister%20of%20social%20welfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreviously%2C%20the%20state%20government%20also%20organised%20an%20awareness%20%3Cem%3Ejatha%20%3C%2Fem%3E(march)%20in%20all%20the%20districts%20from%20January%2026%20to%20February%2023%20with%201%2C025%20special%20events%2C%20covering%205%2C600%20gram%20panchayats.%20As%20per%20the%20government%2C%20the%20march%20featured%2050%20tableaux%2C%20which%20depicted%20contents%20related%20to%20the%20constitution%20and%20other%20connected%20things%20specific%20to%20the%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20event%2C%20Anant%20Nath%2C%20president%20of%20Editors%20Guild%20of%20India%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20fortunate%20that%20we%20have%20such%20an%20elaborate%20constitution%20that%20protects%20civil%20liberty%20and%20freedom.%20While%20we%20celebrate%20the%20Constitution%2C%20we%20need%20to%20strengthen%20%3Cem%3E(sic)%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5Bensure%5D%20that%20constitutional%20values%20are%20disseminated%20to%20the%20last%20mile%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20democracy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708779651000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24173851%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-24-at-5.38.19-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbring-to-power-those-who-respect-the-constitution-karnataka-cm-siddaramaiah%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20chief%20minister%20underlined%20that%20a%20society%20with%20social%20and%20economic%20inequality%20and%20political%20democracy%20can%20succeed%20only%20when%20it%20rests%20on%20the%20foundations%20of%20social%20democracy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbring-to-power-those-who-respect-the-constitution-karnataka-cm-siddaramaiah%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%