tablish%20the%20Palestinian%20State.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fnetanyahu-presents-proposal-for-post-war-gaza%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP%20To%20Release%20List%20Of%20100%20Candidates%20Next%20Week%2C%20PM%20May%20Be%20On%20It%3A%20Sources%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20expected%20announcement%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20next%20month%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20likely%20to%20release%20the%20names%20of%20a%20whopping%20100%20candidates%20on%20Thursday.%20The%20list%20is%20expected%20to%20feature%20both%20of%20the%20party's%20heaviest%20hitters%20-%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20-%20sources%20have%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Central%20Election%20Committee%20of%20the%20BJP%20is%20likely%20to%20meet%20on%20February%2029%2C%20the%20sources%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%20first%20list%20of%20candidates%20may%20be%20made%20after%20that.%20The%20first%20list%20will%20be%20crucial%20because%20the%20ruling%20party%20has%20set%20itself%20a%20mammoth%20target%20of%20winning%20370%20of%20the%20543%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20and%20is%20working%20towards%20securing%20400%20seats%20for%20the%20NDA.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20is%20the%20MP%20from%20Varanasi%2C%20a%20constituency%20he%20has%20won%20twice.%20He%20was%20elected%20with%20a%20huge%20margin%20of%203.37%20lakh%20votes%20in%202014%20and%20had%20increased%20it%20to%204.8%20lakh%20in%202019.%20Amit%20Shah%20had%20contested%20the%202019%20election%20from%20Gandhinagar%2C%20a%20seat%20that%20had%20been%20held%20by%20BJP%20veteran%20LK%20Advani%20until%20then.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20had%20urged%20BJP%20leaders%20and%20workers%20to%20work%20diligently%20towards%20fulfilling%20the%20party's%20