The%20BNS%2C%20set%20to%20replace%20the%20IPC%2C%20has%20reformed%20major%20aspects%20of%20criminal%20laws%20in%20view%20of%20the%20changing%20times%2C%20including%20'community%20service'%20as%20punishment%20for%20minor%20thefts%20and%20adding%20transgenders%20in%20the%20definition%20of%20gender.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdeath-for-lynching-and-rape-of-minor-whats-new-in-latest-criminal-laws-4713607%5C%22%3ENyay%20Sanhita%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20includes%2020%20new%20offences%20like%20organised%20crime%2C%20terrorist%20acts%2C%20mob%20lynching%2C%20hit-and-run%2C%20sexual%20exploitation%20of%20a%20woman%20by%20deceitful%20means%2C%20snatching%2C%20abetment%20outside%20India%2C%20acts%20endangering%20the%20sovereignty%2C%20integrity%2C%20and%20unity%20of%20India%2C%20and%20publication%20of%20false%20or%20fake%20news.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20laws%20will%20widen%20the%20ambit%20of%20what%20constitutes%20terrorism%20and%20provide%20the%20provision%20of%20death%20penalty%20for%20mob%20lynching%20and%20rape%20of%20minors.%20Adultery%2C%20homosexual%20sex%2C%20and%20suicide%20attempts%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20considered%20a%20crimes%20under%20the%20new%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESedition%20law%20has%20been%20repealed%20and%20replaced%20with%20a%20new%20section%20that%20criminalises%20acts%20that%20endanger%20the%20sovereignty%2C%20unity%2C%20and%20integrity%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708775400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F8hulrkec_jail-generic_625x300_21_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnew-criminal-laws-which-replace-penal-code-to-come-into-effect-from-july-1-5118428%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20three%20new%20criminal%20laws%20will%20come%20into%20effect%20from%20July%201%20and%20replace%20the%20country's%20colonial-era%20legislations%2C%20the%20government%20announced%20on%20Saturday.%22%2C%22author