in-india%2F4th-test-england-on-top-after-shoaib-bashir-wrecks-india-in-ranchi%2Farticleshow%2F107968137.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Modi%E2%80%99s%20Call%20for%20370%20Seats%20Is%20Echoed%20by%20Bollywood%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24142346%2Fimage-1870.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theindiacable.com%2Fp%2Firked-by-fascism-charge-modis-censors%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EThe%20India%20Cable%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%93%C2%A0a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%C2%A0The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3Eclick%20here%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20been%20exhorting%20his%20party%20workers%20to%20work%20for%20370%20seats.%20He%20predicts%20the%20BJP%20itself%20will%20get%20that%20number%2C%20and%20along%20with%20the%20allies%2C%20get%20around%20400.%20In%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%20303%20seats%2C%20so%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20pretty%20big%20jump%20of%20about%2067%20seats%2C%20not%20an%20easy%20electoral%20feat%20that%20Modi%20is%20predicting.%20Why%20370%3F%20If%20the%20idea%20is%20to%20touch%20a%20two-third%20majority%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20358%20seats%20should%20be%20enough.%20Nor%20is%20370%20higher%20than%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20400%20plus%20in%20the%201984%20elections.%20So%20how%20did%20Modi%20choose%20the%20number%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20obvious%20really%20%E2%80%93%20370%20is%20also%20the%20number%20of%20the%20Article%20in%20the%20Constitution%20that%20gave%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20its%20special%20status%20within%20the%20Union%20of%20India.%20Getting%20rid%20of%20this%20Article%20was%20the%20first%20major%20decision%20of%20the%20BJP%20government%20after%202019.%20Lest%20voters%20forget%2C%20this%20call%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%20will%20remind%20them%20of%20that.%20And%20the%20media%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20the%20television%20channels%20will%20do%20their%20part%2C%20constantly%20talking%20about%20Mission%20370%20on%20the%20nightly%20news.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20clever%20by-half%20tactic%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20kind%20that%20it%20specialises%20in.%20The%20idea%20is%20to%20always%20remind%20the%20people%20of%20its%20agenda%20and%20its%20%E2%80%98achievements%E2%80%99%2C%20so%20that%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20forget.%20And%20they%20corral%20social%20media%20supporters%2C%20mainstream%20Godi%20media%20and%20of%20course%20fellow%20traveller%20popular%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERight%20on%20cue%2C%20arrives%20%3Cem%3EArticle%20370%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20film%20starring%20Yami%20Gautam%20and%20Arun%20Govil%20(who%20once%20played%20Ram%20in%20the%20TV%20serial%20%3Cem%3ERamayan%3C%2Fem%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20synopsis%20of%20the%20film%20on%20the%20site%20%E2%80%98Book%20my%20Show%2C%E2%80%99%20where%20one%20can%20buy%20tickets%20for%20movies%2C%20reads%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%202016%20Kashmir%20unrest%2C%20a%20young%20local%20field%20agent%2C%20Zooni%20Haksar%2C%20is%20picked%20out%20by%20Rajeshwari%20Swaminathan%20from%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office%20for%20a%20top-secret%20mission.%20Their%20aim%3F%20Cracking%20down%20on%20terrorism%20and%20putting%20an%20end%20to%20the%20billion-dollar%20conflict%20economy%20in%20the%20valley%2C%20by%20doing%20the%20absolute%20impossible%20%E2%80%93%20abrogating%20the%20notorious%20Article%20370.%20That%20too%2C%20without%20spilling%20a%20single%20drop%20of%20innocent%20blood.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELots%20of%20guns%2C%20explosions%2C%20and%20killings%20nonetheless%20follow%2C%20as%20per%20the%20trailer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trailer%20of%20the%20film%20also%20shows%20Gautam%20saying%2C%20earnestly%2C%20%E2%80%9CKashmir%20is%20a%20lost%20case.%20Until%20the%20special%20status%20exists%2C%20we%20cannot%20even%20touch%20them.%20Nor%20will%20they%20allow%20us%20to%20change%20it.%E2%80%9D%20But%20then%20come%20our%20heroes%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20the%20fiery%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20telling%20Parliament%20that%20it%20is%20being%20removed.%20As%20if%20we%2C%20the%20ordinary%20public%2C%20do%20not%20get%20the%20message%2C%20the%20(real)%20prime%20minister%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fit-will-help-people-get-correct-information-pm-modi-on-upcoming-movie-about-article-370-5094687%5C%22%3Eendorsed%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20film.%20Tax%20exemption%20will%20no%20doubt%20follow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENor%20is%20this%20the%20only%20one%20in%20the%20pipeline.%20Waiting%20in%20the%20wings%20is%20%3Cem%3EBastar-The%20Naxal%20Story%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20title%20should%20explain%20what%20this%20could%20be%20about%20%E2%80%93%20if%20you%20have%20doubts%2C%20the%20teasers%2C%20as%20trailers%20are%20called%20now%2C%20will%20clear%20them.%20I%20won%E2%80%99t%20give%20away%20too%20many%20spoilers%2C%20but%20it%20opens%20with%20an%20angry-looking%20woman%20(Adah%20Sharma%2C%20last%20seen%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kerala%20Story%3C%2Fem%3E)%20speaking%20to%20the%20camera%20and%20informing%20us%20that%20the%20wars%20with%20Pakistan%20killed%20only%208%2C738%20Indian%20soldiers%2C%20while%20in%20this%20very%20nation%2C%20Naxals%20have%20killed%20over%2015%2C000%20Indian%20jawans.%20When%20Bastar%20Naxals%20killed%2076%20jawans%20cruelly%2C%20there%20were%20celebrations%20in%20JNU!%20Apparently%20%E2%80%98Left-liberal%20pseudo-intellectuals%E2%80%99%20are%20great%20supporters%20of%20these%20Naxals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20other%20films%20that%20are%20also%20being%20made%2C%20a%20biopic%20of%20V.D.%20Savarkar%20and%20Kangana%20Ranaut%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EEmergency%3C%2Fem%3E.%20No%20doubt%20a%20few%20more%20will%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20such%20overly%20nationalistic%20and%20propaganda%20films%20have%20been%20successful.%20A%20recent%20biopic%20of%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20sank%20without%20a%20trace%2C%20as%20did%20Akshay%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20big-budget%20%3Cem%3ESamrat%20Prithviraj%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20touted%20as%20a%20Hindutva%20film.%20But%20small%20films%20without%20stars%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kashmir%20Files%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kerala%20Story%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20did%20well%20and%20such%20movies%20do%20get%20traction%20on%20social%20media%20even%20if%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20succeed%20at%20the%20box%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20BJP%2C%20however%2C%20flops%20or%20hits%2C%20each%20of%20these%20films%20adds%20to%20the%20noise%20it%20creates%20and%20are%20force%20multipliers.%20They%20confirm%20the%20prejudices%20of%20its%20followers%20and%20potential%20voters%2C%20especially%20from%20a%20younger%20demographic%20who%20will%20probably%20%E2%80%98learn%E2%80%99%20their%20history%20from%20this.%20And%20as%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20open%20support%20for%20%3Cem%3EArticle%20370%3C%2Fem%3E%20shows%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20on%20its%20part%2C%20will%20throw%20its%20full%20weight%20behind%20those%20projects%2C%20such%20as%20Article%20370%2C%20it%20thinks%20will%20help%20its%20mission%20of%20getting%20those%20370%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708774247000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24142346%2Fimage-1870.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fmodis-call-for-370-seats-is-echoed-by-bollywood%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22How%20did%20Modi%20choose%20the%20number%3F%20It's%20obvious%20really%20%E2%80%93%20370%20is%20also%20the%20number%20of%20the%20Article%20in%20the%20Constitution%20that%20gave%20J%26amp%3BK%20its%20special%20status%20within%20the%20Union%20of%20India.%20Getting%20rid%20of%20this%20Article%20was%