ined%20by%20police%20across%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20for%20allegedly%20adopting%20or%20planning%20to%20use%20unfair%20means%20in%20the%20recruitment%20exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccouncing%20the%20decision%2C%20the%20state%20home%20department%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOn%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20information%20and%20facts%20pertaining%20to%20police%20recruitment%20examination%20held%20on%20February%2017%20and%20February%2018%2C%20the%20government%2C%20while%20keeping%20in%20mind%20the%20highest%20standards%20of%20sanctity%20and%20transparency%2C%20has%20decided%20to%20cancel%20the%20examination.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20government%20has%20directed%20the%20recruitment%20board%20to%20register%20an%20FIR%20at%20the%20level%20where%20laxity%20has%20been%20committed%20and%20ensure%20further%20action.%20The%20government%20has%20decided%20to%20get%20the%20matter%20probed%20by%20the%20STF.%20Directions%20have%20also%20been%20issued%20to%20take%20strictest%20action%20against%20the%20guilty%20persons%20and%20organisation%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20statement%2C%20a%20re-examination%20will%20be%20conducted%20within%20six%20months%20and%20UPSRTC%20buses%20will%20ferry%20candidates%20to%20the%20centres%20for%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20development%2C%20senior%20AAP%20leader%20in%20the%20state%20Shekhar%20Dixit%20told%20PTI%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20cannot%20be%20anything%20more%20saddening%20than%20leakage%20of%20examination%20question%20paper.%20Earlier%2C%20question%20paper%20leaks%20were%20unheard%20of%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh...%20The%20leakage%20of%20the%20question%20paper%20proves%20that%20the%20education%20mafia%20is%20still%20very%20strong%20in%20the%20state.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708772940000%2