er%20approach%E2%80%9D%20and%20his%20%E2%80%9Cone-size-fits-all%E2%80%9D%20strategy%20are%20hindering%20India%E2%80%99s%20potential.%20He%20further%20said%20that%20Modi%20poses%20not%20only%20a%20threat%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20progress%20but%20is%20also%2C%20in%20that%20regard%2C%20%E2%80%9Cdangerous.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%2035-minute%20interview%20to%20Karan%20Thapar%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Guha%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CModi%20sees%20himself%20as%20a%20new%20emperor%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommenting%20that%20psychiatrists%20might%20need%20to%20study%20it%2C%20Guha%20spoke%20about%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20delusions%20of%20grandeur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20discussing%20his%20recent%20essay%20on%20foreign%20affairs%2C%20titled%20%E2%80%98How%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20supremacy%20will%20hinder%20his%20country%E2%80%99s%20rise%E2%80%99%2C%20Guha%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20very%20nature%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20authority%2C%20the%20aggressive%20control%20sought%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20his%20party%20over%20a%20staggeringly%20diverse%20and%20complicated%20country%2C%20threatens%20to%20scupper%20India%E2%80%99s%20great-power%20ambitions%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20personality%20and%20style%20of%20government%20%E2%80%9Cis%20jeopardising%20a%20key%20source%20of%20Indian%20strength%3A%20its%20varied%20forms%20of%20pluralism%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20party%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20within%20it%2C%20one%20man%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20are%20judged%20to%20represent%20India%20to%20itself%20and%20to%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20The%20result%20is%20%E2%80%9CHindus%20impose%20themselves%20on%20Muslims%2C%20the%20central%20government%20imposes%20itself%20on%20the%20provinces%2C%20the%20state%20further%20curtails%20the%20rights%20and%20freedoms%20of%20citizens.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20unthinking%20imitation%20of%20Western%20models%20of%20energy-intensive%20and%20capital-intensive%20industrialization%20is%20causing%20profound%20and%2C%20in%20many%20cases%2C%20irreversible%20environmental%20damage.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20there%20is%20a%20huge%20paradox%20which%20Guha%20readily%20accepts.%20Modi%20is%20hugely%20popular%2C%20the%20country%20loves%20him%2C%20and%20he%20is%20very%20likely%20to%20be%20re-elected%20for%20a%20third%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CModi%20remains%20extremely%20popular.%20He%20is%20incredibly%20hardworking%20and%20politically%20astute.%20%5BHe%E2%80%99s%5D%20able%20to%20read%20the%20pulse%20of%20the%20electorate%20and%20adapts%20his%20rhetoric%20and%20tactics%20accordingly.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGuha%20agrees%20this%20means%20we%20have%20a%20master%20politician%20and%20tactician%20ruling%20us%20.%20A%20man%20who%20is%20incredibly%20popular%20and%20powerful.%20But%20he%E2%80%99s%20also%20authoritarian%20and%20majoritarian%20in%20his%20approach.%20And%20he%E2%80%99s%20implementing%20policies%20that%20are%2C%20in%20many%20instances%2C%20disturbing%2C%20divisive%20and%20even%2C%20potentially%2C%20destructive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Febj31A3bT8U%3Fsi%3DdXNRRtV5wNzNLrzK%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708772562000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24163201%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-24-at-15.06.26.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-modis-supremacy-a-threat-to-indias-success-stifling-its-rise-ramachandra-guha%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Guha%20told%20Karan%20Thapar%20that%20Modi's%20'bulldozer%20approach'%20and%20his%20'one-size-fits-all'%20strategy%20are%20hindering%20India's%20potenti