F24135423%2Fimage-1863.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Congress%20and%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20on%20Saturday%20(February%2024)%20ended%20months%20of%20speculation%20surrounding%20its%20fate%20within%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20and%20announced%20seat-sharing%20arrangements%20for%20Delhi%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Goa%2C%20and%20Chandigarh%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20while%20deciding%20to%20fight%20solo%20in%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20Delhi%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20there%20are%20seven%20seats%20on%20which%20AAP%20will%20fight%20on%20four%20seats.%20These%20are%20New%20Delhi%2C%20West%20Delhi%2C%20South%20Delhi%2C%20and%20East%20Delhi.%20Congress%20will%20fight%20on%20three%20seats%20%E2%80%93%20Chandni%20Chowk%2C%20North%20East%2C%20and%20North%20West%2C%E2%80%9D%20announced%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20National%20Alliance%20Committee%20convenor%20Mukul%20Wasnik%20at%20a%20joint%20press%20conference%20of%20the%20two%20parties%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Gujarat%2C%20with%20its%2026%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20Congress%20will%20contest%2024%2C%20while%20AAP%20will%20contest%20two%2C%20including%20Bharuch%20and%20Bhavnagar.%20In%20Haryana%2C%20which%20has%2010%20seats%2C%20Congress%20will%20fight%20on%20the%20nine%20seats%2C%20and%20AAP%20will%20fight%20on%20one%2C%20which%20is%20Kurukshetra.%20Long%20rounds%20of%20talks%20were%20held%20on%20the%20Chandigarh%20seat.%20It%20was%20finally%20decided%20that%20the%20Congress%20candidate%20will%20contest%20this%20seat.%20Detailed%20discussions%20also%20took%20place%20regarding%20Goa%2C%20and%20it%20was%20decided%20that%20both%20seats%20will%20be%20fought%20by%20the%20Congress.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Congress%20chief%20Arvinder%20Singh%20Lovely%2C%20former%20Congress%20general%20secretary%20Deepak%20Babaria%2C%20AAP%20MLAs%20Atishi%2C%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj.%20and%20AAP%20MP%20Sandeep%20Pathak%20were%20present%20at%20the%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20parties%20have%20opted%20to%20contest%20the%20elections%20separately%20in%20Punjab%2C%20where%20AAP%20holds%20power%20and%20Congress%20serves%20as%20the%20Opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20two%20parties%20(AAP%20and%20Congress)%20have%20mutually%20agreed%20to%20contest%20the%20(Lok%20Sabha)%20elections%20in%20Punjab%20separately%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Pathak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAAP%20had%20earlier%20announced%20that%20it%20would%20go%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-aap-to-go-solo-in-punjab-major-setback-for-india%2Farticleshow%2F107580814.cms%5C%22%3Esolo%20and%20fight%20%3C%2Fa%3Eon%20all%2013%20seats%20in%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seat-sharing%20arrangement%20announcement%20comes%20after%20AAP%20had%20alleged%2C%20in%20separate%20press%20conferences%20on%20Thursday%20and%20Friday%2C%20that%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)-led%20Union%20government%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Farvind-kejriwal-bjp-congress-arrest%5C%22%3Eplanning%20to%20arrest%20Delhi%20chief%20minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%2C%20if%20the%20party%20proceeds%20with%20its%20alliance%20with%20the%20Congress%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWasnik%20said%20that%20it%20is%20not%20just%20AAP%20or%20Kejriwal%20who%20are%20facing%20such%20pressure%20tactics%20from%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20not%20limited%20to%20AAP%20or%20AAP%E2%80%99s%20leader%20Arvind%20Kejriwal.%20The%20kind%20of%20circumstances%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20created%20today%20in%20the%20country%20is%20a%20challenge%20to%20democracy.%20Using%20CBI%2C%20ED%2C%20Income%20Tax%20on%20everyone%20to%20put%20pressure%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20politics%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20doing%2C%20which%20is%20dangerous%20for%20Indian%20democracy%2C%20and%20not%20just%20Congress%20and%20AAP%2C%20but%20the%20people%20of%20India%20will%20fight%20against%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seat-sharing%20talks%20between%20the%20two%20parties%20were%20shrouded%20in%20speculation%20for%20months.%20The%20final%20shape%20to%20seat-sharing%20arrangements%20came%20only%20weeks%20after%20AAP%20threw%20the%20gauntlet%20earlier%20this%20month%20and%20offered%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Faap-throws-down-gauntlet-to-congress-seat-sharing-delay%5C%22%3Eonly%20one%20seat%20to%20the%20Congress%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20the%20capital%20while%20saying%20it%20does%20not%20%E2%80%9Cdeserve%20a%20single%20seat%20on%20merit%E2%80%9D.%20While%20the%20national%20leadership%20of%20the%20Congress%20admitted%20to%20a%20delay%20in%20seat-sharing%20talks%2C%20its%20Delhi%20unit%20said%20that%20it%20is%20%E2%80%9Cenergised%E2%80%9D%20to%20fight%20on%20all%20seven%20seats%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPathak%20said%20on%20Saturday%20that%20the%20two%20parties%20have%20set%20aside%20their%20political%20interests%20and%20have%20come%20together%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20nation%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cintention%20of%20this%20alliance%20is%20that%20it%20is%20the%20country%20which%20is%20important%2C%20party%20is%20always%20secondary.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20the%20situation%20that%20the%20country%20is%20going%20through%20%E2%80%93%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20BJP%20government%20is%20finishing%20all%20institutions%20one%20by%20one%2C%20the%20elections%20are%20being%20stolen%2C%20and%20to%20steal%20elections%20and%20win%20elections%2C%20Opposition%20leaders%20are%20being%20put%20in%20jail%20to%20win%20elections%2C%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20injustice%20is%20being%20done%20with%20farmers%2C%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20people%20of%20the%20country%20are%20suffering%20from%20unemployment%20and%20inflation%2C%20the%20country%20needs%20an%20honest%20and%20a%20strong%20alternate.%20Keeping%20this%20in%20mind%2C%20setting%20aside%20our%20own%20political%20interests%20and%20keeping%20in%20mind%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20nation%2C%20we%20have%20come%20together%20in%20this%20alliance%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20election%20will%20not%20be%20fought%20in%20the%20manner%20that%20Congress%20will%20contest%20from%20here%20and%20AAP%20will%20contest%20from%20there.%20INDIA%20will%20contest%20this%20election.%20On%20some%20seats%2C%20Congress%20is%20putting%20its%20candidates%2C%20and%20on%20some%20seats%2C%20AAP%20is%20fielding%20candidates.%20I%20believe%20that%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20calculations%20will%20be%20overturned%20after%20this%20alliance%20and%20we%20will%20fight%20and%20win%20these%20elections%20with%20the%20support%20of%20the%20people%20of%20this%20country.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708763330000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24135423%2Fimage-1863.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-and-aap-seal-seat-sharing-deal-for-delhi-haryana-gujarat-goa-but-to-go-solo-in-punjab%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AAP%20MP%20Sandeep%20Pathak%20said%20that%20the%20two%20parties%20have%20set%20aside%20their%20political%20interests%20as%20the%20'intention%20of%20this%20alliance%20is%20that%20it%20is%20the%20country%20which%20is%20important%2C%20the%20party%20is%20always%20secondary.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-and-aap-seal-seat-sharing-deal-for-delhi-haryana-gujarat-goa-but-to-go-solo-in-punjab%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Assam%20Repeals%20Muslim%20Marriages%20and%20Divorces%20Act%3B%20BJP%20Cites%20Intent%20to%20Implement%20UCC%20in%20State%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F08144104%2FGFlamxXa0AAQFxW.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party-led%20Assam%20government%20on%20Friday%20(February%2023)%20approved%20the%20repeal%20of%20the%20Assam%20Muslim%20Marriages%20and%20Divorces%20Registration%20Act%2C%201935%2C%20in%20what%20an%20Assam%20minister%20termed%20as%20a%20significant%20step%20forward%20towards%20implementing%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20(UCC)%20in%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20chief%20minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20claimed%20that%20the%20decision%20will%20help%20the%20government%20prevent%20child%20marriages%20in%20the%20state%2C%20his%20cabinet%20minister%20Jayanta%20Malla%20Baruah%20laid%20out%20a%20larger%20motivation%20behind%20the%20move%2C%20that%20is%20to%20implement%20the%20UCC%20in%20Assam.%20Baruah%20also%20said%20that%20the%20existing%20law%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccolonial%20Act%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETaking%20to%20X%20(formerly%20called%20Twitter)%2C%20Sarma%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9COn%20February%2023%2C%20the%20Assam%20cabinet%20made%20a%20significant%20decision%20to%20repeal%20the%20age-old%20Assam%20Muslim%20Marriages%20and%20Divorces%20Registration%20Act.%20This%20act%20contained%20provisions%20allowing%20marriage%20registration%20even%20if%20the%20bride%20and%20groom%20had%20not%20reached%20the%20legal%20ages%20of%2018%20and%2021%2C%20as%20required%20by%20the%20law.%20This%20move%20marks%20another%20significant%20step%20towards%20prohibiting%20child%20marriages%20in%20Assam.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhimanta-chartered-flights-helicopter-assam-assembly%5C%22%3ERs%2058%2C23%2C07%2C104%3A%20Public%20Money%20Spent%20on%20CM%20Himanta%2C%20Other%20VIPs%E2%80%99%20Air%20Travel%2C%20According%20to%20Assam%20Govt%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E