2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhow-the-union-govt-is-slowly-but-surely-blurring-indias-federal-structure%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPart%20IV%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-sabka-saath-sabka-vikas-hoax%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPart%20V%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20parts%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwhy-election-commissions-faqs-on-evm-vvpats-dont-clear-cloud-of-suspicion-over-electoral-process%5C%22%3Eone%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fevms-and-vvpats-why-suspicions-persist-and-wont-subside-yet%5C%22%3Etwo%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20this%20series%2C%20I%20sought%20to%20probe%20deeper%20into%20several%20answers%20which%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20has%20provided%20in%20its%20revised%20set%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eci.gov.in%2Fevm-faq-new%5C%22%3E100%20%3C%2Fa%3Efrequently%20asked%20questions%20to%20demonstrate%20how%20unsatisfactory%20they%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ECI%20publicised%20these%20revised%20FAQs%20on%20its%20website%20in%20January%202024%20with%20the%20objective%20of%20clarifying%20all%20doubts%20about%20these%20electoral%20machines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20300px)%2085vw%2C%20300px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F03150954%2FPrism.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F03150954%2FPrism.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F03150954%2FPrism-150x150.png%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-691446%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%3EWhen%20compared%20with%20the%20information%20contained%20in%20publicly%20available%20official%20documents%2C%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20claims%20about%20the%20design%2C%20and%20functioning%20of%20electronic%20voting%20machines%20(EVMs)%20and%20Voter%20Verifiable%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail%20(VVPAT)%20units%20raise%20more%20suspicion%20instead%20of%20resolving%20persistent%20doubts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20write-up%2C%20I%20address%20a%20few%20more%20of%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20claims%20in%20light%20of%20patent-related%20documents%20and%20the%20information%20disclosed%20in%20response%20to%20formal%20requests%20for%20information%20made%20under%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20Act%2C%202005%20(RTI%20Act)%20with%20particular%20focus%20on%20the%20following%20grey%20areas%20in%20the%20FAQs%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EWhy%20are%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20Technical%20Expert%20Committee%20members%20also%20listed%20as%20VVPAT%20inventors%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0How%20transparent%20is%20the%20independent%20review%20of%20EVM-VVPATs%20conducted%20by%20the%20Standardisation%20Testing%20and%20Quality%20Certification%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhy%20are%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20Technical%20Expert%20Committee%20members%20also%20listed%20as%20VVPAT%20inventors%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ECI%20has%20claimed%20that%20the%20EVM-VVPAT%20combo%20is%20manufactured%20by%20two%20Central%20Public%20Sector%20Undertakings%20(CPSUs)%2C%20under%20the%20guidance%20of%20Technical%20Experts%20Committee%20which%20it%20has%20constituted.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20response%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3EFAQ%20%237%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhere%20are%20the%20EVMs%20manufactured%3F%20Are%20they%20imported%3F%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20ECI%20has%20stated%20as%20follows%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3EAns.%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3EEVMs%2FVVPATs%20are%20not%20imported%20but%20indigenously%20designed%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Emanufactured%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eby%20two%20Public%20Sector%20Undertakings%20(PSUs)%20namely%20Bharat%20Electronics%20Limited%20(BEL)%2C%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20and%20Electronics%20Corporation%20of%20India%20Limited%20(ECIL)%2C%20under%20the%20Department%20of%20Atomic%20Energy%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eunder%20the%20guidance%20of%20the%20Technical%20Experts%20Committee%20(TEC)%20constituted%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFurther%2C%20at%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3EFAQ%20%2368%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20ECI%20admirably%20rises%20to%20the%20defence%20of%20the%20competence%20and%20credibility%20of%20the%20TEC%20members%20as%20follows%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFAQ%2068.%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EExperts%E2%80%9D%20have%20declared%20that%20the%20ECI%20machines%20are%20non%20tamperable%20and%20safe%20but%20this%20does%20not%20make%20the%20EVM%2B%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%5Bsic%5D%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3ENone%20of%20the%20ECI%20experts%20have%20credentials%20in%20computer%20security%20and%20the%20majority%20of%20them%20are%20not%20even%20computer%20scientists%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20In%20addition%20to%20experts%20the%20ECI%20is%20also%20dependent%20on%20many%20other%20entities%20and%20organisations-including%20hardware%20manufacturers%2C%20software%20developers%20and%20testers%2C%20system%20assemblers%2C%20and%20un-modelled%20custody%20chains%20for%20the%20integrity%2C%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20its%20machines%20and%20is%20thus%20not%20entirely%20in%20control.%20In%20this%20situation%20what%20is%20the%20need%20to%20use%20EVMs%20for%20elections%20in%20India%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAns.%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3EComments%20on%20ECI%20experts%20are%20uncalled%20for%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20EVM%20detractors%2C%20self-appointed%20technical%20experts%20and%20certain%20social%20media%20personnel%20have%20repeatedly%20failed%20to%20realise%20that%20the%20EVMs%20cannot%20be%20compared%20to%20a%20computer%20which%20runs%20on%20an%20operating%20system.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20microcontrollers%20of%20EVMs%20and%20VVPATs%20run%20on%20a%20specific%20program%20designed%20to%20faithfully%20record%20the%20voters%E2%80%99%20choice%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20the%20EVM%20is%20a%20truthful%20machine%20has%20been%20proved%20over%20decades%20of%20usage%20through%20changes%20in%20several%20governments%20at%20the%20state%20and%20central%20level%2C%20whenever%20the%20public%20wanted%20to.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20EVM%20has%20made%20elections%20safe%20and%20virtually%20eradicated%20booth%20capturing%20by%20limiting%20the%20rate%20of%20vote%20casting%20to%20four%20votes%20a%20minute%20and%20thus%20significantly%20increasing%20the%20time%20required%20for%20stuffing%20false%20votes.%20Invalid%20votes%20a%20bane%20of%20the%20paper%20ballot%20system%20was%20at%20times%20greater%20than%20the%20winning%20margins%20and%20have%20been%20completely%20eliminated%20by%20the%20EVMs.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVote%20cast%20is%20verifiable%20by%20voter%20on%20VVPAT%20and%20the%20Control%20Unit-VVPAT%20vote%20count%20matches%20are%20done%20on%20well-established%20principles%20of%20statistics%20to%20provide%20a%20very%20high%20level%20of%20confidence%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20its%20hurry%20to%20dispel%20all%20doubts%20about%20EVMs%20and%20VVPATs%2C%20the%20ECI%20has%20left%20the%20first%20sentence%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3EFAQ%20%2368%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20hanging%2C%20but%20let%20me%20not%20quibble%20about%20this%20minor%20issue.%20In%20response%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3EFAQ%20%231%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20an%20EVM%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20ECI%20hyperlinks%20a%20portion%20of%20its%20answer%20to%20a%20page%20in%20its%202021%20Status%20Paper%20on%20EVMs%20and%20VVPATs%20containing%20the%20names%20of%20the%20TEC%20members%20and%20their%20appointed%20role%20(see%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3EImages%201%26amp%3B2%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20below)%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24081649%2FScreenshot-2024-02-24-at-8.15.36-1024x659.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24081649%2FScreenshot-2024-02-24-at-8.15.36-1024x659.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24081649%2FScreenshot-2024-02-24-at-8.15.36-300x193.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24081649%2FScreenshot-2024-02-24-at-8.15.36.png%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698613%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22541%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EImages%201%20and%202%3A%20Pages%20hyperlinked%20to%20FAQ%20%231%20explaining%20the%20membership%20and%20role%20of%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20TEC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOriginally%20constituted%20in%201990%2C%20the%20membership%20changed%20about%2015%20years%20later.%20The%20current%20TEC%20was%20constituted%20in%202010%20with%20the%20following%20experts%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EProfessor%20D.T.%20Shahani%20of%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20Delhi%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EProfessor%20Rajat%20Moona%20of%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20Bhilai%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EProfessor%20Dinesh%20Sharma%20of%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20Bombay%3B%20and%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EProfessor%20A.K.%20Agarwala%20of%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20Delhi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20will%20not%20question%20their%20scholarship%20or%20competence%20as%20I%20am%20not%20qualified%20to%20do%20so.%20However%2C%20as%20a%20voting%20and%20taxpaying%20citizen%20of%20India%20I%20have%20every%20right%20to%20ask%20this%20fundamental%20question.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhy%20are%20these%20current%20TEC%20Members%20also%20included%20in%20the%20list%20of%20%E2%80%98inventors%E2%80%99%20of%20VVPAT%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20336px)%2085vw%2C%20336px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24082019%2FScreenshot-2024-02-24-at-8.19.48-433x1024.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22336%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24082019%2FScreenshot-2024-02-24-at-8.19.48-433x1024.png%20433w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24082019%2FScreenshot-2024-02-24-at-8.19.48-127x300.png%20127w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24082019%2FScreenshot-2024-02-24-at-8.19.48.png%20508w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698614%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22795%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EImages%203%20and%204%3A%20Declaration%20of%20%E2%80%98Inventorship%E2%80%99%20submitted%20by%20BEL%20to%20obtain%20a%20patent%20for%20the%20VVPAT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20Inventorship%20Declaration%20Form%20filed%20with%20the%20Patents%20Controller%20while%20applying%20for%20a%20patent%2C%20BEL%20listed%2012%20individuals%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9CInventors%E2%80%9D%20of%20VVPAT.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20All%20four%20TEC%20Members%20are%20also%20listed%20as%20Inventors%20of%20the%20VVPAT%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20according%20to%20its%20Proof-of-Right%20document%20submitted%20to%20the%20Patents%20Controller%20along%20with%20its%20application%2C%20BEL%20calls%20itself%20only%20the%20%E2%80%9CApplicant%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20VVPAT%20patent%20but%20not%20its%20%E2%80%9CInventor%E2%80%9D%20(see%20Image%205%20below).%20All%2012%20individuals%20listed%20above%20are%20shown%20as%20%E2%80%9CInventors%E2%80%9D%20here%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20names%20of%20all%20four%20TEC%20Members%20are%20found%20in%20this%20list%20(see%20Images%206-7%20below).%20This%20document%20also%20bears%20the%20signature%20of%20one%20of%20the%20TEC%20Members%20(see%20Image%207%20below).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20role%20of%20the%20TEC%20is%20clearly%20specified%20in%20ECI%E2%80%99s%202021%20EVM%20Status%20Paper%20as%20follows%20(see%20Image%202%20above)%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ei.%20Give%20technical%20advice%20to%20build%20specifications%20and%20design%20of%20newer%20versions%20of%20EVMs%2FVVPATs%20that%20they%20incorporate%20latest%20technology%20both%20in%20hardware%20and%20software%20design%20and%20improving%20robustness%20against%20tampering.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eii.%20Examine%20design%20proposals%20of%20manufacturers%20of%20EVMs%20and%20offer%20recommendations%20for%20improvement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eiii.%20Mentor%20designs%20process%20wherever%20asked.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eiv.%20Examine%20concerns%20raised%20on%20EVMs%20tamperability.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ev.%20Any%20other%20advice%20that%20Commission%20%5BECI%5D%20may%20seek%20or%20any%20other%20technical%20work%20that%20the%20Commission%20may%20entrust%20from%20time%20to%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFurther%20in%20response%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3EFAQ%20%2333%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(see%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3ESection%20II%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20below)%20the%20ECI%20states%20that%20the%20TEC%20also%20conducts%20an%20independent%20audit%20of%20the%20voting%20systems%20design.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECan%20TEC%20Members%20sit%20in%20judgement%20over%20their%20own%20invention%3F%20Is%20this%20not%20a%20huge%20conflict%20of%20interests%3F%20Is%20it%20not%20reasonable%20to%20expect%20that%20inventors%20will%20defend%20their%20invention%20against%20all%20objections%20raised%20by%20anybody%20and%20everybody%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20fact%2C%20in%20December%202020%2C%20the%20Patent%20Examiner%20submitted%20a%20report%20objecting%20to%20BEL%E2%80%99s%20claims%20that%20the%20VVPAT%20was%20its%20unique%20invention%20and%20completely%20dissimilar%20to%20other%20electronic%20voting%20and%20vote%20counting%20machines%20being%20used%20elsewhere%20on%20the%20planet.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24083602%2FScreenshot-2024-02-24-at-8.34.08-1024x474.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24083602%2FScreenshot-2024-02-24-at-8.34.08-1024x474.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24083602%2FScreenshot-2024-02-24-at-8.34.08-300x139.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24083602%2FScreenshot-2024-02-24-at-8.34.08.png%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698615%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22389%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EImages%205%2C%206%20and%207.%20Pages%201-3%20of%20the%20Proof-of-Right%20document%20BEL%20submitted%20along%20with%20the%20VVPAT%20patent%20application.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Patent%20Examiner%20also%20remarked%20that%20the%20only%20innovative%20thing%20about%20the%20VVPAT%20claim%20was%20its%20software%20but%20under%20Section%203(k)%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Patents%20Act%2C%201970%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Esoftware%20is%20not%20patentable.%20BEL%20sought%20extra%20time%20to%20make%20its%20submissions%20in%20response%20to%20these%20objections%20and%20eventually%20obtained%20the%20patent%20in%20May%202022.%20The%20Patent%20Examiner%E2%80%99s%20report%20and%20BEL%E2%80%99s%20submissions%20are%20all%20available%20on%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fipindia.nic.in%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDid%20the%20TEC%20Members%20give%20any%20advice%20to%20overcome%20the%20Patent%20Examiner%E2%80%99s%20objection%3F%20The%20patent%20records%20by%20their%20very%20nature%20will%20not%20reveal%20such%20details.%20Such%20information%20will%20be%20available%20in%20the%20records%20held%20by%20BEL%20and%20the%20ECI.%20However%2C%20neither%20of%20them%20has%20disclosed%20any%20details%20about%20the%20role%20that%20TEC%20Members%20played%20in%20overcoming%20the%20Patent%20Examiner%E2%80%99s%20objections.%20In%20fact%2C%20none%20of%20the%20TEC%20reports%20with%20regard%20to%20VVPATs%20are%20available%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20In%20response%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthe-anatomy-of-an-electronic-voting-machine-what-we-know-and-what-we-dont%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emy%20RTI%20intervention%20of%20March%202019%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20EC%20furnished%20TEC%20reports%20pertaining%20to%20EVMs%20only%2C%20prepared%20between%201990%20and%202013%20and%20no%20further.%20This%20is%20another%20instance%20of%20the%20ECI%20and%20BEL%20putting%20away%20crucial%20technical%20information%20including%20TEC%20recommendations%20about%20VVPATs%20in%20a%20black%20box.%20The%20FAQs%20are%20simple%20inadequate%20for%20arriving%20at%20an%20informed%20opinion%20about%20the%20EVM-VVPAT%20combo.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20how%20is%20this%20different%20from%20the%20patent%20that%20BEL%20and%20ECIL%20obtained%20in%202006%20for%20their%20EVMs%3F%20The%20name%20of%20BEL%E2%80%99s%20inventor%2C%20Rajagopalan%20Jagannathan%2C%20is%20mentioned%20in%20the%20patent%20summary%20on%20the%20IP%20India%20website%20(see%20Image%208%20below).%20ECIL%20also%20mentions%20only%20one%20individual%2C%20Gadde%20Raja%20Koteswara%20Rao%2C%20an%20employee%2C%20as%20the%20inventor%20of%20its%20EVM%20(see%20Image%209%20below).%20Neither%20individual%20ever%20served%20on%20any%20of%20the%20earlier%20TECs%20(see%20Image%201%20above).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TEC%E2%80%99s%20role%20at%20that%20point%20of%20time%20was%20limited%20to%20providing%20technical%20advice%20and%20there%20was%20no%20occasion%20for%20any%20conflict%20of%20interests%20to%20arise.%20However%2C%20there%20is%20a%20clear%20case%20of%20conflict%20of%20interests%20with%20the%20current%20TEC%20members%20vis-%C3%A0-vis%20their%20role%20as%20co-Inventors%20of%20the%20VVPAT.%20Strangely%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20does%20not%20talk%20about%20any%20of%20these%20issues%20in%20its%20FAQs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24084032%2FScreenshot-2024-02-24-at-8.37.48-1024x624.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24084032%2FScreenshot-2024-02-24-at-8.37.48-1024x624.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24084032%2FScreenshot-2024-02-24-at-8.37.48-300x183.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24084032%2FScreenshot-2024-02-24-at-8.37.48.png%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698616%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22512%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EImages%208%20and%209.%20Patent%20documents%20showing%20the%20names%20of%20the%20EVM%20inventors%20of%20BEL%20and%20ECIL.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHow%20transparent%20is%20the%20independent%20review%20of%20EVM-VVPATs%20conducted%20by%20STQC%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ECI%20explains%20the%20systems%20put%20in%20place%20for%20an%20independent%20review%20of%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20EVM%20and%20VVPAT%20combo%20in%20response%20to%20FAQs%20%2333%20and%20%2372%20as%20follows%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3EQ%2033.%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Can%20the%20ECI%20implement%20an%20independent%20review%20system%20to%20review%20the%20voting%20system%20and%20the%20integrity%20of%20election%20process%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAns.%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20voting%20system%20designs%20go%20through%20an%20independent%20review%20and%20even%20an%20independent%20audit%20by%20Technical%20Expert%20Committee.%20Various%20design%20details%20are%20also%20available%20on%20the%20site%20at%20a%20level%20that%20the%20stakeholders%20may%20be%20interested%20in.%20The%20outcomes%20accepted%20by%20voters%20and%20candidates%20are%20the%20biggest%20form%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ereview%20(Annexure-II%20and%20Annexure-III).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ECI-EVM%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Evoting%20system%20goes%20through%20an%20independent%20review%20by%20way%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethird%20party%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3E(STQC)%20checks%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20They%20also%20go%20through%20independent%20audit%20by%20various%20political%20parties%2Fcandidates%2Ftheir%20representatives%20like%20in%20mock%20polls.%20The%20processes%20are%20well%20defined%20and%20are%20put%20on%20the%20website%20of%20the%20ECI%20for%20public%20view.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3EQ%2072.%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20While%20banning%20electronic%20voting%2C%20the%20German%20Constitutional%20Court%20made%20the%20following%20observation%3A%20The%20use%20of%20voting%20machines%20which%20electronically%20record%20the%20voters%E2%80%99%20votes%20and%20electronically%20ascertain%20the%20election%20result%20only%20meets%20the%20constitutional%20requirements%20if%20the%20essential%20steps%20of%20the%20voting%20and%20of%20the%20ascertainment%20of%20the%20results%20can%20be%20examined%20reliably%20and%20without%20any%20specialist%20knowledge%20of%20the%20subject%E2%80%A6%20The%20legislature%20is%20not%20prevented%20from%20using%20electronic%20voting%20machines%20in%20elections%20if%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20reliable%20examination%20of%20correctness%2C%20which%20is%20constitutionally%20prescribed%2C%20is%20safeguarded.%20A%20complementary%20examination%20by%20the%20voter%2C%20by%20the%20electoral%20bodies%20or%20the%20general%20public%20is%20possible%20for%20example%20with%20electronic%20voting%20machines%20in%20which%20the%20votes%20are%20recorded%20in%20another%20way%20beside%20electronic%20storage.%20How%20are%20ECI%20EVMs%20different%20from%20the%20voting%20systems%20banned%20by%20the%20German%20Constitutional%20Court%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAns.%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3EAcross%20the%20world%2C%20both%20paper%20ballot%20voting%20system%20as%20well%20as%20EVMs%20are%20used%20for%20conducting%20elections%20as%20per%20the%20preference%20and%20mandate%20of%20the%20authorities%20concerned.%20The%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20is%20a%20Constitutional%20Body%20mandated%20to%20conduct%20elections%20to%20State%20Legislature%2C%20both%20the%20houses%20of%20the%20Parliament%20and%20the%20offices%20of%20the%20President%20of%20India%20and%20Vice-President%20of%20India%2C%20as%20per%20Act%20and%20Rules%20passed%20by%20the%20Parliament%20of%20India.%20Use%20of%20ECI-EVMs%20for%20conducting%20elections%20in%20India%20is%20approved%20by%20the%20Parliament%20and%20upheld%20by%20various%20High%20Courts%20and%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EECI%20EVMs%20are%20manufactured%20by%20central%20government%20public%20sector%20undertakings%20in%20a%20secure%20manufacturing%20facility.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ERigorous%20third-party%20testing%20is%20carried%20out%20by%20STQC%20(Standardization%20Testing%20and%20Quality%20Certification)%20at%20the%20manufacturing%20premises%20before%20acceptance%20and%20dispatch%20to%20various%20states%20of%20deployment%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Stringent%20and%20elaborate%20protocols%20as%20mandated%20by%20ECI%20are%20followed%20during%20EVM%20movement%2C%20storage%2C%20and%20deployment.%20The%20German%20Constitutional%20Court%20made%20its%20observation%20in%20the%20context%20of%20EVMs%20used%20in%20German%20elections%20and%20in%20relation%20to%20German%20law.%20Indian%20EVMs%20are%20robust%20and%20implement%20technologies%20and%20processes%20which%20are%20different%20and%20noncomparable.%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20and%20various%20High%20Courts%20have%20time%20and%20again%20scrutinised%20the%20machines%20and%20have%20reposed%20their%20confidence%20and%20faith%20in%20ECI%20EVMs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20sum%20and%20substance%20of%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20responses%20to%20the%20FAQs%20above%20is%20that%20STQC%20is%20the%20agency%20that%20is%20officially%20tasked%20with%20the%20review%20and%20testing%20of%20EVMs%20and%20VVPATs.%20STQC%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stqc.gov.in%2Fabout-stqc%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EStandardisation%20Testing%20and%20Quality%20Certification%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E)%20is%20a%20Directorate%20attached%20to%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%20which%20provides%20quality%20assurance%20services%20in%20the%20are%20of%20Electronics%20and%20IT%20through%20a%20country-wide%20network%20of%20laboratories%20and%20centres.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20STQC%20claims%20that%20all%20of%20its%20financial%20obligations%20are%20met%20through%20budgetary%20support%20provided%20by%20the%20government%20of%20India%2C%20so%20it%20is%20essentially%20an%20agency%20of%20the%20Union%20government.%20The%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stqc.gov.in%2Fetdc-hyderabad-4%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESTQC%20also%20claims%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20ECI%20has%20identified%20its%20Electronics%20Test%20and%20Development%20Centre%20(ETDC)%20Hyderabad%20as%20the%20testing%20lab%20for%20third%20party%20testing%20of%20EVMs%20and%20VVPATs.%20However%2C%20no%20further%20information%20about%20what%20kinds%20of%20testing%20STQC%20does%20is%20available%20on%20its%20website.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20June%202019%2C%20an%20RTI%20application%20was%20submitted%20to%20the%20STQC%20seeking%20information%20about%20the%20names%20and%20designations%20of%20the%20STQC%20team%20which%20conducted%20testing%20and%20evaluation%20of%20the%20firmware%20of%20the%20EVMs%20and%20VVPATs%20used%20during%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%3B%20the%20dates%20on%20which%20such%20testing%20was%20carried%20out%20and%20the%20geographical%20location%20where%20such%20testing%20was%20done%3B%20the%20total%20number%20of%20BEL%20and%20ECIL%20manufactured%20machines%20which%20the%20STQC%20team%20tested%20and%20evaluated%2C%20a%20copy%20of%20all%20manuals%20and%20standard%20operating%20procedures%20(SOPs)%20which%20contains%20the%20methodology%20to%20be%20used%20for%20such%20testing%20purposes%3B%20and%20a%20clear%20description%20of%20the%20instruments%20used%20for%20such%20testing%2C%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20test%20reports%20prepared%20by%20the%20STQC%20team.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EData%20about%20the%20number%20of%20EVM-VVPATs%20which%20showed%20mismatch%20with%20the%20reference%20firmware%20and%20other%20kinds%20of%20errors%20detected%20during%20the%20testing%20was%20also%20sought.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20STQC%20rejected%20all%20these%20queries%20invoking%20Section%208(1)(d)%20of%20the%20RTI%20Act%20which%20protects%20information%20that%20is%20in%20the%20nature%20of%20commercial%20confidence%20or%20trade%20secrets%20or%20intellectual%20property%20rights%20(IPR)%20whose%20disclosure%20would%20harm%20the%20competitive%20position%20of%20a%20third%20party%20(see%20Images%2010%20and%2011%20below).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24085226%2FScreenshot-2024-02-24-at-8.51.53-1024x649.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24085226%2FScreenshot-2024-02-24-at-8.51.53-1024x649.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24085226%2FScreenshot-2024-02-24-at-8.51.53-300x190.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24085226%2FScreenshot-2024-02-24-at-8.51.53.png%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698617%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22532%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EImages%2010%20and%2011%3A%20STQC%E2%80%99s%20reply%20to%20RTI%20queries%20about%20EVM%20and%20VVPAT%20third%20party%20testing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20this%20reply%20was%20challenged%20before%20the%20first%20appellate%20authority%20of%20STQC%2C%20he%20upheld%20the%20denial%20on%20grounds%20of%20commercial%20confidence%20without%20specifying%20whose%20interests%20were%20being%20protected%20%E2%80%93%20STQC%E2%80%99s%2C%20ECI%E2%80%99s%2C%20or%20those%20of%20BEL%20and%20ECIL.%20So%2C%20this%20matter%20was%20escalated%20to%20the%20Central%20Information%20Commission%20(CIC)%20the%20same%20year.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CIC%20took%20two%20years%20to%20hear%20this%20case.%20During%20the%20hearing%20STQC%20opposed%20the%20second%20appeal%20claiming%20that%20testing%20services%20are%20provided%20by%20levying%20charges%20on%20the%20requestor%20for%20such%20services%2C%20so%20the%20information%20sought%20in%20the%20RTI%20application%20belongs%20to%20the%20service%20requestor.%20Disclosure%20would%20harm%20the%20competitive%20position%20of%20BEL%20and%20ECIL%2C%20STQC%20argued%20(see%20Image%2012%20below).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20502px)%2085vw%2C%20502px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24090912%2FScreenshot-2024-02-24-at-9.08.31.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22502%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24090912%2FScreenshot-2024-02-24-at-9.08.31.png%20846w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24090912%2FScreenshot-2024-02-24-at-9.08.31-300x294.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698618%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22493%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EImage%2012%3A%20STQC%E2%80%99s%20counter%20to%20the%20second%20appeal%20submitted%20to%20the%20CIC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmong%20the%20several%20counter%20arguments%20that%20I%20submitted%20to%20the%20CIC%2C%20I%20had%20contended%20that%20there%20is%20no%20possibility%20of%20any%20harm%20arising%20on%20account%20of%20the%20information%20disclosure%20because%20the%20two%20CPSUs%20have%20a%20ECI-guaranteed%20duopoly%20on%20the%20EVM-VVPAT%20market%20in%20India.%20In%20July%202021%2C%20the%20CIC%20directed%20that%20information%20regarding%20testing%20dates%20and%20quantities%20of%20machines%20tested%20be%20disclosed%20as%20no%20harm%20would%20be%20caused.%20It%20refused%20to%20direct%20disclosure%20of%20the%20names%20and%20designations%20of%20the%20members%20of%20STQC%E2%80%99s%20testing%20team%20holding%20that%20it%20is%20in%20the%20nature%20of%20commercial%20confidence.%20Instead%20of%20deciding%20on%20their%20correctness%20despite%20having%20the%20power%20to%20do%20so%2C%20the%20CIC%20merely%20directed%20STQC%20to%20re-examine%20its%20replies%20to%20other%20queries.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202021%20STQC%20sent%20a%20revised%20reply%20(see%20Images%2013%20and%2014%20below)%20providing%20access%20only%20to%20the%20period%20during%20which%20the%20machines%20were%20tested%20at%20the%20factory%20premises%20of%20BEL%20and%20ECIL.%20Despite%20the%20CIC%E2%80%99s%20finding%20that%20statistical%20information%20about%20the%20number%20of%20EVMs%20and%20VVPATs%20tested%20does%20not%20attract%20any%20exemption%2C%20STQC%20rejected%20this%20information%20under%20Section%208(1)(e)%20now%2C%20claiming%20fiduciary%20relationship%20with%20BEL%20and%20ECIL.%20It%20also%20rejected%20access%20to%20manuals%20and%20SOPs%20used%20for%20testing%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20STQC%20said%20that%20no%20errors%20or%20mismatch%20were%20found%20in%20the%20firmware%20used%20in%20the%20EVM-VVPAT%20combo%20when%20compared%20with%20the%20reference%20firmware.%20It%20did%20not%20provide%20a%20direct%20reply%20to%20the%20query%20about%20other%20kinds%20of%20errors%20in%20the%20machines%20that%20might%20have%20been%20detected.%20Instead%2C%20the%20STQC%20said%20that%20no%20failures%20were%20observed%20related%20to%20the%20firmware%20of%20EVMs%20and%20VVPATs%20it%20tested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24091502%2FScreenshot-2024-02-24-at-9.14.24-1024x710.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24091502%2FScreenshot-2024-02-24-at-9.14.24-1024x710.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24091502%2FScreenshot-2024-02-24-at-9.14.24-300x208.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24091502%2FScreenshot-2024-02-24-at-9.14.24.png%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698619%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22582%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EImages%2013%20and%2014%3A%20STQC%E2%80%99s%20revised%20RTI%20reply%20after%20the%20CIC%20remanded%20the%20case%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhy%20is%20STQC%E2%80%99s%20revised%20RTI%20reply%20problematic%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFirst%2C%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3ESTQC%20transgressed%20the%20CIC%E2%80%99s%20order%20by%20withholding%20information%20about%20the%20number%20of%20machines%20it%20tested%20even%20though%20the%20CIC%20directed%20its%20disclosure.%20But%20let%20us%20leave%20that%20aside%20for%20the%20time%20being.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESecond%2C%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3ESTQC%20provided%20only%20the%20period%20during%20which%20it%20had%20tested%20the%20VVPATs%20of%20both%20companies.%20It%20remained%20silent%20about%20tests%20conducted%20on%20Control%20Units%20(CUs)%20and%20Ballot%20Units%20(BUs)%20even%20though%20similar%20information%20was%20sought%20about%20the%20testing%20of%20EVMs.%20Why%20is%20this%20problematic%3F%20This%20is%20because%20of%20the%20large%20number%20of%20EVMs%20and%20VVPATs%20that%20were%20found%20defective%20prior%20to%20and%20during%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EECI%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3E%20FAQ%20%2399%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3Edeals%20with%20this%20issue%20as%20follows%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3EQ%2099.%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20It%20is%20claimed%20that%20higher%20percentage%20of%20EVMs%20and%20VVPATs%20got%20defective%20during%20First%20Level%20Checking%20of%20EVMs%20and%20VVPATs%20pertaining%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%202019.%20What%20action%20taken%20by%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20to%20reduce%20the%20percentage%20of%20defects%20of%20EVMs%20and%20VVPATs%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAns%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20In%20General%20Elections%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20simultaneous%20elections%20in%20the%20States%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Sikkim%20and%20Odisha%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E37%2C377%20Ballot%20Units%20(1.8%25)%2C%2057%2C775%20Control%20Units%20(3.8%25)%20and%2085%2C905%20VVPATs%20(5.4%25)%20were%20rejected%20during%20First%20Level%20Checking%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20during%20actual%20poll%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%202019%2C%20replacement%20rates%20were%20BU%20%E2%80%93%200.74%25%2C%20CU%20%E2%80%93%200.79%25%20and%20VVPAT%20%E2%80%93%203.36%25%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20every%20election%2C%20an%20analysis%20of%20non-functional%20EVMs%20and%20VVPATs%20is%20carried%20out%20as%20an%20integral%20part%20for%20enhancing%20the%20performance%20of%20EVMs%20and%20VVPATs%20to%20reduce%20replacement%20rates%20during%20actual%20poll.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPost%20General%20Election-2019%2C%20the%20Technical%20Expert%20Committee%20(TEC)%20carried%20out%20an%20exhaustive%20analysis%20along%20with%20Bharat%20Electronics%20Ltd%20(BEL)%20and%20Electronics%20Corporation%20of%20India%20Ltd%20(ECIL).%20Analysis%20got%20delayed%20due%20to%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20period.%20In%20analysis%2C%20it%20was%20concluded%20that%20some%20corrective%20actions%20are%20required%20to%20be%20taken%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3Eto%20reduce%20the%20replacement%20rate%20of%20M3%20VVPATs%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20to%20ensure%20voter%20is%20not%20put%20to%20any%20inconvenience.%20%3Cem%3E(emphasis%20added)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EM2%20model%20machines%2C%20used%20during%20General%20Election-2019%2C%20had%20been%20discontinued%20as%20their%20economic%20life%20completed.%20M2-M3%20VVPATs%2C%20used%20along%20with%20M2%20EVMs%20during%20General%20Election-2019%2C%20are%20upgraded%20to%20M3%20VVPATs%2C%20as%20originally%20planned%20to%20ensure%20that%20they%20are%20compatible%20with%20M3%20EVMs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EECI%E2%80%99s%20response%20to%20the%20above%20FAQ%20sounds%20very%20bureaucratic.%20Tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20machines%20%E2%80%93%20BUs%2C%20CUs%20and%20VVPATs%20which%20STQC%20said%20it%20had%20checked%20between%202017%20and%202019%2C%20did%20not%20pass%20the%20first%20level%20check%20(FLC)%20right%20up%20to%20the%20eleventh%20hour%20when%20Phase%201%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20began%20mid-March%20in%202019.%20There%20were%20more%20replacements%20of%20these%20machines%20during%20the%20actual%20polls%20conducted%20in%20seven%20phases.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20press%20release%20dated%C2%A0March%2010%2C%202019%2C%20(see%20Image%2015%20below)%20the%20ECI%20published%20the%20total%20number%20of%20BUs%2C%20CUs%20and%20VVPATs%20that%20were%20to%20be%20deployed%20for%20the%202019%20elections%20(along%20with%20general%20elections%20to%20four%20States%20and%20bye-elections%20to%2034%20vacant%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20other%20states%20and%20UTs).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20549px)%2085vw%2C%20549px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24091817%2FScreenshot-2024-02-24-at-9.18.04%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22549%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https