0elections%2C%20nevertheless%20had%20to%20be%20replaced%20during%20the%20actual%20polls.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20voters%20and%20taxpayers%2C%20we%20must%20ask%20ourselves%2C%20if%20this%20were%20the%20track%20record%20of%20companies%20selling%20electronic%20calculators%20in%20the%20market%2C%20would%20consumers%20find%20those%20machines%20reliable%20enough%20to%20buy%3F%20Would%20consumers%20like%20to%20spend%20their%20money%20on%20calculators%20that%20are%20likely%20to%20have%20even%20a%20less%20than%201%25%20probability%20of%20being%20defective%20or%20malfunctioning%3F%20No%2C%20we%20would%20want%20every%20calculator%20we%20buy%20to%20work%20perfectly.%20Why%20adopt%20a%20different%20standard%20for%20EVMs%20and%20VVPATs%3F%20This%20is%20the%20elephant%20in%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20room%20filled%20with%20100%20FAQs%20which%20it%20simply%20does%20not%20address.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20I%20will%20demonstrate%20the%20depth%20and%20breadth%20of%20this%20defective%2Fmalfunctioning%20problem%20in%20the%20next%20instalment%20of%20this%20series.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20kinds%20of%20tests%20did%20STQC%20conduct%20on%20ECIL%E2%80%99s%20EVM%2FVVPAT%20combo%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20two%20identical%20RTI%20applications%20submitted%20to%20BEL%20and%20ECIL%20submitted%20in%20March%202019%2C%20I%20had%20sought%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20reports%20of%20the%20tests%20conducted%20on%20the%20EVMs%20and%20VVPATs%20in%20addition%20to%20other%20information.%20While%20BEL%20rejected%20this%20RTI%20query%20by%20invoking%20commercial%20confidence%2C%20ECIL%20rejected%20it%20on%20grounds%20of%20national%20security.%20Both%20matters%20were%20escalated%20to%20the%20CIC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20later%2C%20the%20CIC%20remanded%20the%20matter%20back%20to%20the%20CPSUs%20to%20decide%20the%20RTI%20applications%20afresh%20even%20though%20it%20has%20the%20power%20to%20examine%20the%20correctness%20of%20their%20