0not%20be%20shared%20as%20well%3F%20Why%20did%20so%20many%20thousands%20of%20CUs%20fail%20to%20perform%20before%20and%20during%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20despite%20passing%20the%20STQC%E2%80%99s%20tests%3F%20The%20ECI%20has%20much%20more%20to%20answer%20because%20crucial%20information%20about%20the%20manner%20of%20tests%20conducted%20on%20the%20EVM-VVPAT%20combo%20remain%20hidden%20in%20a%20black%20box.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwhy-election-commissions-faqs-on-evm-vvpats-dont-clear-cloud-of-suspicion-over-electoral-process%5C%22%3Ebegan%20part%20one%20of%20this%20series%20by%20recounting%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20exasperation%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20number%20of%20attempts%20being%20made%20by%20various%20petitioners%20to%20seek%20an%20urgent%20hearing%20with%20regard%20to%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20were%20conducted%20with%20the%20help%20of%20these%20machines.%20The%20apex%20court%E2%80%99s%20Bench%20apparently%20remarked%2C%20%E2%80%9CIs%20there%20no%20end%20to%20these%20suspicions%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20All%20that%20I%20can%20humbly%20say%20after%20five%20years%20of%20multiple%20RTI%20interventions%20that%20there%20is%20simply%20not%20enough%20information%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20to%20end%20these%20suspicions.%20This%20is%20because%20the%20ECI%20and%20the%20EVM-VVPAT%20manufacturing%20companies%20have%20not%20adequately%20discharged%20their%20burden%20of%20proving%20their%20claims%20about%20these%20machines%20by%20putting%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20crucial%20official%20documents.%20The%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20clarifications%20in%20its%20revised%20FAQs%20hint%20at%20the%20existence%20of%20a%20whole%20lot%20of%20information%20that%20is%20unfortunately%20black%20boxed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EVenkatesh%20Nayak%20is%20Director%2C%20Commonwealth%20Human%20Rights%20Initiative%2C%20New%20Delhi.%20All%20facts%20narrated%20above%20are%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20Views%20expressed%20are%20personal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708746907000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09193848%2FScreenshot-2023-11-09-at-7.38.08%25E2%2580%25AFPM_cleanup.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fevms-and-vvpats-why-the-suspicions-will-not-abate-yet%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20clarifications%20in%20its%20revised%20FAQs%20hint%20at%20the%20existence%20of%20a%20whole%20lot%20of%20information%20that%20is%20unfortunately%20black%20boxed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fevms-and-vvpats-why-the-suspicions-will-not-abate-yet%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22At%20Home%20and%20Outside%2C%20Women%20Are%20Constantly%20Made%20to%20Do%20Unpaid%20Work%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F24075257%2FUntitled-design-4-2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAhead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20unemployment%20unites%20India%20as%20few%20things%20do.%20Its%20relevance%20is%20as%20much%20as%20it%20was%20in%20successive%20assembly%20polls%20and%20yet%20as%20an%20issue%2C%20it%20has%20been%20often%20ignored.%20Why%20is%20most%20of%20India%20out%20of%20work%3F%20How%20do%20unemployed%20Indians%20live%3F%20Why%20is%20the%20work%20available%20not%20enough%20to%20earn%20a%20livelihood%3F%20What%20makes%20an%20Indian%20that%20much%20more%20likely%20to%20get%20or%20not%20get%20work%3F%20The%20Wire%20unveils%20a%20series%20that%20explores%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20poll%20issues%20of%20our%20time.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENine%20in%20ten%20woman%20domestic%20workers%20are%20compelled%20to%20do%20additional%2C%20unpaid%20work%20beyond%20what%20they%20agreed%20to%20%E2%80%93%20work%20that%20they%20estimate%20is%20worth%20between%20Rs.%201%2C500%20to%20Rs.%203%2C000%20a%20month%20in%20lost%20wages.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20third%20of%20women%20MGNREGS%20workers%20in%20Uttarakhand%20said%20the%20work%20expected%20from%20them%20is%20so%20intense%20that%20they%20have%20to%20get%20family%20members%20to%20help%2C%20for%20which%2C%20again%2C%20there%20is%20no%20payment.%20In%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20nearly%20three%20quarters%20of%20women%20fishworkers%20said%20they%20were%20doing%20more%20work%20now%20for%20the%20same%20wage%20than%20when%20they%20started%20work.%20Moreover%2C%20all%20this%20unpaid%20labour%20is%20on%20top%20of%20the%20existing%20unfair%20burdens%20of%20unpaid%20care%20work%20in%20the%20home.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20317px)%2085vw%2C%20317px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F20144212%2FIMG_2915-1-746x1024.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22317%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F20144212%2FIMG_2915-1-746x1024.jpg%20746w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F20144212%2FIMG_2915-1-219x300.jpg%20219w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F20144212%2FIMG_2915-1.jpg%20874w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697965%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22435%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty.%20Photo%3A%20Intifada%20P.%20Basheer%20and%20Azam%20Abbas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnsurprisingly%2C%20more%20than%20two%20thirds%20of%20women%20workers%20reported%20that%20they%20feel%20exhausted%20every%20day%2C%20and%20in%20Delhi%2040%25%20of%20women%20workers%20say%20they%20get%20less%20than%20six%20hours%20of%20sleep.%20Where%20they%20are%20able%20to%20share%20the%20care%20work%20in%20their%20homes%2C%20they%20do%20so%20much%20more%20with%20their%20girl%20children%20than%20they%20do%20with%20either%20their%20spouses%20or%20their%20boy%20children.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20problem%20is%20made%20worse%20by%20shortcomings%20in%20public%20services.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20For%20instance%2C%20not%20being%20able%20to%20access%20health%20care%20quickly%20and%20affordably%20meant%20that%20family%20members%20are%20often%20only%20treated%20when%20they%20are%20seriously%20ill%20%E2%80%93%20increasing%20the%20likelihood%20of%20disability%20and%20long%20recovery%20periods%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20imposes%20additional%20burdens%20on%20women%20(public%20health%20insurance%20schemes%20such%20as%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20can%20help%20reduce%20hospitalisation%20expenditures%2C%20but%20do%20not%20help%20with%20illnesses%20that%20do%20not%20require%20hospitalisation).%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20public%20day%20care%20for%20children%20means%20women%20workers%20have%20to%20either%20take%20their%20children%20with%20them%20to%20work%20or%20leave%20them%20with%20other%20women%20relatives%2C%20which%20also%20increases%20their%20care%20workload.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20limited%20supplies%20available%20from%20the%20public%20distribution%20system%20in%20most%20states%20increase%20prices%20and%20require%20women%20to%20take%20time%20out%20to%20either%20access%20rations%20or%20find%20cheaper%20supplies.%20The%20same%20is%20true%20of%20fuel%2C%20given%20how%20expensive%20cooking%20gas%20has%20become.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20of%20these%20factors%20were%20worsened%20by%20the%20pandemic%2C%20which%20simultaneously%20hit%20family%20incomes%20and%20increased%20care%20burdens%20on%20women.%20The%20weakness%20of%20labour%20law%20means%20that%20workers%20are%20unable%20to%20resist%20demands%20for%20unpaid%20work%20from%20employers%2C%20because%20they%20fear%20for%20their%20jobs%20and%20often%20have%20no%20effective%20legal%20recourse%20to%20protect%20their%20rights.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20are%20some%20of%20the%20findings%20of%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fissin.org%2Fresearch%2Freports%2Funpaid-work-and-women-workers-a-growing-crisis%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estudy%20by%20the%20Institute%20of%20Social%20Sciences%2C%20New%20Delhi%20and%20the%20Rosa%20Luxemburg%20Stiftung%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20conducted%20across%20four%20regions%20of%20three%20states%20(Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Uttarakhand%20and%20Delhi).%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUsing%20a%20survey%20of%20over%202%2C500%20women%2C%20followed%20by%20focus%20group%20discussions%20and%20individual%20interviews%2C%20the%20study%20found%20that%20unpaid%20work%20is%20a%20huge%20burden%20on%20women%20workers%20%E2%80%93%20affecting%20their%20health%20and%20their%20ability%20to%20secure%20their%20rights.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20study%20makes%20certain%20policy%20recommendations%20that%20aim%20to%20address%20these%20key%20problems.%20It%20calls%20for%20the%20expansion%20of%20anganwadis%2C%20primary%20health%20care%2C%20and%20public%20distribution%20of%20food%20items%20to%20reduce%20the%20care%20burden%20on%20women%20workers.%20The%20study%20notes%20that%20the%20MGNREGS%2C%20notwithstanding%20its%20shortcomings%2C%20also%20provided%20a%20framework%20for%20women%20workers%20to%20attempt%20to%20secure%20their%20rights%20(which%20was%20particularly%20evident%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu).%20Therefore%2C%20it%20calls%20for%20rationalisation%20of%20rates%20under%20the%20MGNREGS%2C%20the%20provision%20of%20mandatory%20child%20care%20under%20the%20scheme%20(which%20is%20already%20required%20by%20law%2C%20but%20often%20not%20implemented)%2C%20redressal%20of%20other%20implementation%20issues%20in%20the%20MGNREGS.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20address%20the%20legal%20disempowerment%20of%20women%20workers%2C%20it%20recommends%20a%20labour%20law%20framework%20for%20domestic%20workers%20rights%2C%20registration%20boards%20for%20women%20workers%20on%20the%20lines%20of%20construction%20welfare%20boards%2C%20and%20an%20urban%20employment%20guarantee%20on%20the%20same%20lines%20as%20the%20MGNREGS.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOverall%2C%20while%20recent%20policies%20such%20as%20laws%20around%20sexual%20harassment%20and%20domestic%20violence%20have%20helped%20protect%20women%20in%20their%20homes%20and%20workplace%2C%20the%20economic%20and%20legal%20disempowerment%20of%20women%20workers%20has%20meant%20they%20continue%20to%20face%20unfair%20burdens%20of%20unpaid%20work.%20The%20hope%20is%20that%20changes%20in%20some%20key%20policies%20can%20be%20a%20start%20on%20the%20path%20to%20addressing%20this%20problem.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EShankar%20Gopalakrishnan%20is%20a%20faculty%20member%20of%20the%20Institute%20of%20Social%20Sciences.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cem%3ESmita%20Gupta%20is%20a%20consulting%20advisor%20to%20the%20institute%E2%80%99s%20research%20team%20and%20an%20expert%20on%20political%20economy%20and%20development%20issues.%20%3Ci%3EThe%20institute%20is%20grateful%20to%20the%20Rosa%20Luxemburg%20Stiftung%20for%20supporting%20this%20study.%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708741425000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F20144212%2FIMG_2915-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fwomen-labour-india-mgnregs-unpaid%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Using%20a%20survey%20of%20over%202%2C500%20women%2C%20followed%20by%20focus%20group%20discussions%20and%20individual%20interviews%2C%20a%20study%20found%20that%20unpaid%20work%20is%20a%20huge%20burden%20on%20women%20workers%20%E2%80%93%20affecting%20their%20health%20