dream%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20having%20to%20give%20up%2C%20clouded%20Akshay%E2%80%99s%20mind.%20During%20this%20time%20he%20was%20also%20offered%20a%20job%2C%20but%20a%20gut%20feeling%20told%20him%20he%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20give%20up%20on%20his%20dream%20just%20yet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%2C%20the%20next%20day%2C%20with%20a%20Rs%2010%2C000%20investment%2C%20Akshay%20decided%20to%20turn%20his%20shed%20outside%20his%20home%20into%20his%20lab.%20%E2%80%9CI%20purchased%20a%20pump%20from%20Amazon%2C%20a%20temperature%20sensor%20and%20I%20set%20up%20a%20bioreactor%20in%20my%20house.%20I%20had%20the%20know-how%20to%20prepare%20the%20fertiliser.%20I%20decided%20to%20do%20it%20at%20home.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20the%20weeks%20that%20followed%2C%20Akshay%20went%20around%20collecting%20old%20wood%2C%20and%20soil%20from%20different%20types%20of%20environments%20%E2%80%94%20from%20harsh%20climates%2C%20marshy%20areas%20to%20loamy%20soil%20and%20cow%20dung.%20The%20first%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337129%2Feroponics-tower-planter-for-balcony-garden-by-iit-kanpur-startup-macrogardens%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebatch%20of%20fertiliser%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20prepared%20weighed%203%20kg.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-9-1708604729.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Navyakosh%20fertiliser%20bridges%20the%20gap%20between%20chemical%20and%20organic%20fertilisers%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-9-1708604729.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fagriculture-9-1708604729-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fup