0the%20two%20and%20a%20half%20months%20driving%20through%2016%20countries%2C%20Daman%20and%20his%20family%20have%20watched%20the%20world%20through%20a%20window%2C%20literally%20and%20metaphorically.%20%E2%80%9CLandscapes%20changed%2C%20time%20zones%20shifted%2C%20we%20watched%20it%20all%20in%20real-time%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20gazing%20off%20into%20the%20distance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20I%E2%80%99m%20sure%20that%20he%20is%20mentally%20still%20in%20those%20lands%20he%20speaks%20of%20so%20fondly.%20But%20how%20much%20did%20this%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340559%2Ftravel-tips-for-people-with-disability-to-make-travelling-safe-where-to-book%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emind-boggling%20trip%20cost%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20you%20may%20ask%3F%20%E2%80%9CRoughly%20the%20cost%20of%20a%20Mercedes%2C%E2%80%9D%20Daman%20says%20cheekily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAround%20the%20world%20in%2076%20days%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20child%2C%20Daman%20never%20saw%20Lal%20Pari%20as%20a%20car.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20mother%20would%20tell%20me%20these%20stories%20of%20how%20Lal%20Pari%20had%20superpowers%20and%20could%20come%20to%20save%20us%20whenever%20we%20needed.%20I%20grew%20up%20believing%20that.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20my%20favourite%20memories%20have%20been%20in%20this%20car%2C%E2%80%9D%20Daman%20adds.%20These%20include%20trips%20to%20the%20zoo%20when%20he%20was%20younger%2C%20family%20trips%20when%20he%20was%20older%2C%20and%20eventually%20his%20marriage.%20So%2C%20it%20only%20seemed%20right%20that%20the%20car%20was%20his%20companion%20on%20this%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338637%2Fmeghalaya-homestay-travellers-nest-vacation-adventure-lovers-mawlyngbna-caving-canyoning-treks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edreamy%20adventure%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp